  "pages": [
    "<div class=\"metadata-header\" style=\"display:none;\">informatica|Git-Github|comandos|configuracoes</div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17798034084640.3470167256210709\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 61px; top: 65px; width: 676px; height: 431px; z-index: 17;\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(205, 92, 92);\"><strong><em>dnf install git</em></strong></span></p><p></p><p>git --version (lista a vesrao que ta instalada )</p><p></p><p>definir nome do usuário</p><p>git config --global <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\">user.name</a> \"Radames Langner\"</p><p></p><p>mostra nome do usuário \"<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\">user.name\".</a></p><p>git config <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\">user.name</a></p><p><br></p><p>definir e-mail</p><p>git config --global <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.email\">user.email</a> \"<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"mailto:radahmes@gmail.com\">radahmes@gmail.com</a>\"</p><p></p><p>mostra o e-mail do usuário \"user.email\".</p><p>git config <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\">user.email</a></p><p><br></p><p>define editor</p><p>git config --global core-editor vscode</p><p>git config <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\">user.name</a></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>show list</p><p><br></p><p>git config --list</p></div>",
    "<div class=\"metadata-header\" style=\"display:none;\">informatica|Git-Github|comandos|configuracoes</div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17798037426500.07187349609606275\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 63px; top: 67px; width: 620px; height: auto; z-index: 15;\"><p>show list</p><p></p><p>git config --list</p><p></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\">user.name</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\">=Radames Langner </span><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\"><br></span><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"mailto:user.email=radahmes@gmail.com\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\">user.email=radahmes@gmail.com</span></a><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\"><br></span>Criar repositorio (mkdir projeto)</p><p><br>Cria a pasta que deseja cirar pelo sistema ou pelo prompt ou terminal</p><p>Dentro da pasta que criada e que se deseja iniciar , com o comando :</p><p><br>git init - inicia a pasta, gera arquivo .git</p><p><br></p></div>",
    "<div class=\"metadata-header\" style=\"display:none;\">informatica|Git-Github|comandos|configuracoes</div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799099346560.40939985237728005\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 25px; top: 64px; width: 672px; height: 24px; z-index: 8;\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(205, 92, 92); font-size: 18px;\"><strong><em>git remote add origin URL </em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>(associa repositório remoto ao repositório local)</strong></span></p></div>",
    "<div class=\"metadata-header\" style=\"display:none;\">informatica|Git-Github|comandos|configuracoes</div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799102110370.11562393123153192\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 37px; top: 61px; width: 328px; height: 40px; z-index: 4;\"><h1>Chave pública github</h1><p></p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799102346660.2684204935893396\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 38px; top: 131px; width: 688px; height: 360px; z-index: 55;\"><h2><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1. Verificar se a chave existe</span></h2><p></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">ls -la ~/.ssh</span></p><p>                         id_ed25519</p><p>                         id_<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://ed25519.pub\">ed25519.pub</a></p><ul><li><p><code>id_ed25519</code> → <strong>chave privada</strong> (NUNCA compartilhar)</p></li><li><p><code>id_ed25519.pub</code> → <strong>chave pública</strong> (essa vai para o GitHub)</p></li></ul><p></p><h2><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2. Criar a chave SSH</span></h2><p></p><p>ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C \"<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"mailto:seu-email@example.com\">seu-email@example.com</a>\"</p><p></p><p>Cria as chave citadas acima.</p><p></p><p><code>Especificando o tipo -t ed25519 comentando -C \"ajuda a identificar\"</code></p><p><code>Senha ajuda a proteger a chave sem senha só precionar enter</code></p><p></p></div>",
    "<div class=\"metadata-header\" style=\"display:none;\">informatica|Git-Github|comandos|configuracoes</div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799109949050.3207222351468624\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 26px; top: 234px; width: 512px; height: 272px; z-index: 31;\"><h2><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3. Adicionar no GitHub</span></h2><p></p><p>Entre no:  <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"decorated-link\" href=\"https://github.com/settings/keys?utm_source=chatgpt.com\">GitHub SSH Keys </a></p><p></p><p>Clique em:   New SSH key</p><p>Preencha:  <strong>Title    </strong>Algo descritivo, por exemplo: Fedora 44 KDE</p><p></p><p><strong>Key type </strong>Authentication Key</p><p></p><p><strong>Key </strong>Cole a chave pública (<code>id_ed25519.pub</code>).</p><p>Depois: Add SSH key</p><p></p><p>Pode pedir senha do GitHub.</p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799111316520.8842444439199989\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 30px; top: 69px; width: 744px; height: 136px; z-index: 13;\"><h2><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3. Copiar a chave pública</span></h2><p></p><p>Mostre a chave:</p><pre><code>cat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub</code></pre><p>Vai aparecer algo parecido com:</p><pre><code>ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAI.... seu-email@pc</code></pre><p></p></div>",
    "<div class=\"metadata-header\" style=\"display:none;\">informatica|Git-Github|comandos|configuracoes</div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799119508590.10608112963072336\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 27px; top: 79px; width: 696px; height: 152px; z-index: 12;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong><em>Teste de conexão </em></strong></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 215, 0); font-family: monospace;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\"> ssh -T </span><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"mailto:git@github.com\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\">git@github.com</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\">Enter passphrase for key '/home/rada/.ssh/id_ed25519': &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\">Hi radameslangner! You've successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access. </span><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\"><br><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\"><br></span></p></div>"
  ],
